tags.note: No separate name, part of Victoria Terrace

tags.name: Kerrison Villas
tags.note:name: Street appears to have two names, according to street signs. Kerrison Villas to the east side, Kerrison Place to the West.

tags.name: Pope's Lane
tags.note: The Victoria County History says there was Pope's Lane as early as 1423. There was also Pope's Cross at the west end, where it joined Drum Lane (now South Ealing Road).
